title: Doctor Who 2005 s04e17e18 The End of Time Fan Edit
description:
This is a fan edit of The End of Time that gets rid of all the unnecessary and weird stuff: no more magically resurrected  (itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s left ambiguous), cannibal, flying Master, no more Wilfred magically finding the Doctor (the Doctor phones him in a scene I patched together), no more the Master copying himself into every human (now he just controls the minds of the people in the Mansion.)
